msg: * tools/cvs2svn/cvs2svn.py

author: kfogel
msg: Simplify some interfaces:
* tools/cvs2svn/cvs2svn.py
(SymbolicNameTracker.fill_name, SymbolicNameTracker.fill_tag,
SymbolicNameTracker.fill_branch): Don't bother to take svn_rev and
svn_path anymore; we don't need to check that they got created,
as the load will fail in a debuggable way if they weren't anyway.

author: kfogel
msg: Add --dump-only option to cvs2svn.py:
* tools/cvs2svn/cvs2svn.py
(SVNROOT): Remove this constant.
(usage): Document new option.
(main): Initialize new option to 0 in ctx, parse for it in getopt,
and do a consistency check on options afterwards.
(pass5): Don't load the dumpfile if ctx.dump_only is true.
